4680/the-2016-top-10-esports-draft |title=The 2016 top 10 esports draft |work=[[ESPN]] |first=Tyler |last=Erzberger |date=June 27, 2016 |accessdate=June 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107080634/http://www.espn.co.uk/esports/story/_/id/16454680/the-2016-top-10-esports-draft |archivedate=November 7, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eurogamer alien swarm release\">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/valve-releases-alien-swarm-for-free |title=Valve releases Alien Swarm for free |work=[[Eurogamer]] |first=Wesley |last=Yin-Poole |date=July 8, 2014 |accessdate=May 15, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213036/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/valve-releases-alien-swarm-for-free |url-status=live |archivedate=March 3, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eurogamer cg\">{{cite web |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news190504thisandthat |title=This And That: Wednesday News Roundup |first=Tom |last=Bramwell |date=May 19, 2004 |website=[[Eurogamer]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eurogamer cs neo\">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/article_47678 |title=Counter-Strike hits the arcades Namco in apparent lapse of concentration |work=[[Eurogamer]] |first=Martin |last=Taylor |date=April 3, 2003 |accessdate=May 15, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515193120/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/article_47678 |archivedate=May 15, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eurogamer csnz\">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-08-07-counter-strike-nexon-zombies-heads-to-steam |title=Counter-Strike Nexon: Zombies heads to Steam |work=[[Eurogamer]] |first=Robert |last=Purchese |date=June 24, 2010 |accessdate=May 15, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411122215/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-08-07-counter-strike-nexon-zombies-heads-to-steam |url-status=live |archivedate=April 11, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eurogamer css mac\">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.n