 (musician)|Pole]]\n* [[Prefuse 73]]\n* [[Nobukazu Takemura|Takemura]]\n* [[Copenhagen sound]]\n* [[Mille Plateaux]]\n* [[Mira Calix]]\n* [[CoH (musician)|CoH]]\n* [[Blevin Blechtum]]\n* [[Ekkehard Ehlers|Ehlers]]\n* [[Philip Jeck]]\n* [[Mike Ladd]]\n* [[Matthew Shipp]]\n* [[Dev79]]\n* [[Hecate]]\n* Demotic\n* [[Oye (album)|Oye]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Live reviews'''\n* [[Mutek|Micro_MUTEK 2003 Festival]]\n* [[Lali Puna]], [[Opiate (band)|Opiate]], [[Pulseprogramming]] and [[Styrofoam (artist)|Styrofoam]]\n* [[Keith Rowe]], [[Toshimaru Nakamura]], [[Nmperign]] and [[Le Quan Ninh]]\n* [[Kling Klang]], [[Macrocosmica]] and [[The Beale]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Gear reviews'''\n* [[Tassman|AA Tassman 3]]\n* [[Mackie|Mackie Control]] and [[JLCooper|JLCooper CS-32]]\n* [[Traktor|NI Traktor 2]]\n* [[GMedia|GMedia Oddity]]\n* [[Steinberg|Steinberg Plex]]\n* [[Ohmforce|Ohmforce Ohmboyz]]\n* [[Ableton Live|Ableton Live 2]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n=== Issue 11 ===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n'''Features'''\n* [[Kid 606]]\n* [[Mu-Ziq]]\n* [[Broadcast (band)|Broadcast]]\n* [[Gold Chains]]\n* [[Si Begg]]\n* [[Alejandra & Aeron]]\n* Unit and [[Co.ad.audio]]\n* [[Tied & Tickled Trio]]\n* [[Mariana Rosenfeld]]\n* [[End Records|End]]\n* [[EU (musician)|EU]]\n* [[Jason Forrest|Donna Summer]]\n* [[Ellen Allien]]\n* [[Miles TIlman]]\n* [[Cex (musician)|Cex]]\n* [[Ui (band)|Ui]]\n* [[Davide Balula]]\n* [[D\u00e9sormais]]\n* [[Midwest Product]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Live reviews'''\n* [[Mutek|MUTEK 2004 Festival]]\n* [[All Tomorrow's Parties (music festival)|All Tomorrow's Parties]]\n* [[Sonar Festival]]\n* [[DAT Politics]], [[Keith Whitman]] and [[Misterinterrupt]]\n* [[Kid 606]], [[DJ /rupture]], [[Pole (musician)|Pole]] and [[Kevin Martin (English musician)|The Bug]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Gear reviews'''\n* [[Reaktor|NI Reaktor 4]]\n* [[Roland|Roland VariOS Open System Module]]\n* [[Moog synthesizer|Moog Modular V]]\n* [[Cakewalk|Cakewalk Project 5]]\n* [[Clavia|Clavia Nord Lead 2X]]\n* [[Steinberg|Steinberg Xphrase]]\n* [