oto|Carsten Nicolai]]\n* [[Janek Schaefer]], [[Duplo Remote]] and Antenna Farm\n<br />\n'''Book reviews'''\n* ''The Ambient Century'', Mark Prendergast\n* ''MP3: The Definitive Guide'', [[Scot Hacker]]\n* ''Modulations'', edited by [[Peter Shapiro (journalist)|Peter Shapiro]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Gear reviews'''\n* [[Propellerheads Reason]]\n* [[Spektral Delay|NI Spektral Delay]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n=== Issue 07 ===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n'''Features'''\n* [[Autechre]]\n* [[Matthew Herbert|Herbert]]\n* [[Bogdan Raczyinski]]\n* [[Janek Schaefer]]\n* James Coleman\n* [[Manual (musician)|Manual]]\n* [[Nic Endo]]\n* [[Rafael Toral]]\n* Dan Abrams\n* [[Gridlock (band)]]\n* [[Twine (musician)|Twine]]\n* [[Safety Scissors]]\n* [[Andreas Tilliander]]\n* [[Paul Lansky]]\n* [[Smalltown Supersound]]\n* [[Defocus]]\n* [[Susumu Yokota]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Live reviews'''\n* [[Sin Festival]]\n* [[Tortoise]], [[Nobukazu Takemura]], [[Scott Herren|Prefuse 73]], [[Mr. Lif]] and [[DJ Muet]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Gear reviews'''\n* [[Traktor DJ Studio|NI Traktor]]\n* [[Reaktor|NI Reaktor 3]]\n* [[Mixman DM2]]\n* [[Sonar|Cakewalk Sonar XL]]\n* [[Tassman|AA Tassman 2]]\n* [[Fruity Loops|ILS Fruity Loops 3]]\n* [[Absynth|NI Absynth]]\n* [[DR-008|Fxpansion DR-008]]\n* [[iSynth|Cycling74 MES iSynth]]\n* [[Waldorf Attack|Steinberg Waldorf Attack]]\n* [[Bombthatbeat|ProjectOne Bombthatbeat 1.5]]\n* [[EVP88|Emagic EVP88]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n=== Issue 08 ===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n'''Features'''\n* [[Boards of Canada]]\n* [[Faust (musician)]]\n* [[The Black Dog]]\n* [[Drexiciya]]\n* [[Keith Fullerton Whitman|Hrvatski]]\n* [[Jamie Lidell|Super_Collider]]\n* [[Anti-Pop Consortium]]\n* [[Nanoloop]]\n* [[Venetian Snares]]\n* [[DJ Vadim]]\n* [[Tim Hecker]]\n* [[Greg Davis (musician)|Greg Davis]]\n* [[Telefon Tel Aviv]]\n* [[Somatic Responses]]\n* [[Sogar]]\n{{col-3}}\n'''Live reviews'''\n* [[All Tomorrow's Parties (music festival)|All Tomorrow's Parties - Los Angeles]]\n* [[Adult]], [[I Am Spoonbender]], [[The Fai